{
  "stem": "11144.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm sure that they are suffering from-- from that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we belonged to the Jewish Center, and--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they [INAUDIBLE], they grew up in Teaneck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they went to Hebrew schools.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They-- they both went to Israel, as young-- you know, as young children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So, you know, we were-- I mean, when-- when they got to a point when they started understanding something, we joined the Center because before we didn't, and we started celebrating holidays.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- so they, you know, as far as that is concerned, they grew up-- I know that, in Teaneck High, even when my son was in high school, they did have some tapes of, you know, about the Holocaust, and sometimes he would come home and he would tell us about it.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know whether he could stomach it, or he could think about it or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know, because he is sensitive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But yesterday-- Sunday, when I spoke to him and we told him that, you know, that you're coming here today, he was very excited about it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right, well, it's interesting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the beginning, when we came here-- now, my husband had a big family here because his father's brothers and sisters emigrated here way when, in the beginning of the century, I guess.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, maybe, [INAUDIBLE], yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were here and we have not met-- some of the cousins we still never met.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they just had no interest in refugees, and that's what, probably in their mind, I mean, we were looked upon as.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we have cousins here around the corner, with whom now, we are, you know, friendly.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
